title: Start
body:
Jake: Hey Jenny! What a coincidence! Let's play!

		Jenny: It Jake, my cousin.

		Jake: Looking at your lunch box, you must be on your way to your grandma's house.

		Jake: Let's play for a while now, you can always go there later.

		Jenny: Should I play with Jake? But I need to send food to grandma on time.

		[[Hey Jake! Sorry, I need to send food to grandma. Let's play later.|DontPlayWithJake]]
[[Hey, Jake! Long time no see. Sure, let's play!|PlayWithJake]]

title: DontPlayWithJake
body:
Jenny: My mom told me to send the lunch as soon as possible, so this is my responsible to reach grandma's house on time. 

		Jenny: Let's have a lunch there and play later!

title: PlayWithJake
body: Jenny: Oh no! My Grandma is still waiting for my food!
